data.description: Spectacular 3 Bdrm 2.5 Ba ranch home nestled on a gorgeous 1.6 acre lot in Genoa Twsp w/convenient access to highways, shopping and Brighton/Howell areas. Features include: Abundance of natural light t/o * Kitchen w/granite counters, glass tile backsplash, S.S. appliances * Fabulous 19x16 cathedral ceiling great room w/gas fireplace and access out to the 35x12 rear deck * Spacious primary bedroom w/ensuite bath and access to the rear deck * Hall bath features zero clearance roll in shower * Partially finished bsmnt w/25x22 Rec Rm, spotless storage areas, High efficiency furnace and Wtr Htr * Attached 31 x 20 side entry 3 car garage w/epoxy finished floor * 50x24 Pole barn w/cement floor, wood fired heater and 220V power * Tear-Off Roof replaced 2022 * Neutral decor t/o * Immed Occupancy!
